    "originContent": "### **Advanced Features**",
    "translatedContent": "### **高度な機能**"
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "EQv+YFsS3OWqhlEf3Hw8fRY//WlPOsqGbCgkmPD4HPA=",
    "originContent": "- **Smart Disable Options**:",
    "translatedContent": "- **スマート無効化オプション**:"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "bLEhMoFbB3HnEb4UnoJMkW76i/i7Y262YM/EFBlQjCc=",
    "originContent": "  - **\"Only if unused/not connected\"** - Don't disable WiFi, Bluetooth, or Location if actively in use",
    "translatedContent": "  - **「未使用/未接続の場合のみ」** - 使用中のWiFi、Bluetooth、または位置情報は無効化しない"
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "9cWuarRZjlN0U3qbnj+KroCstk/eUfTVp/XObwKBSIY=",
    "originContent": "  - **\"Only if not already enabled\"** - Prevent connection resets by not re-enabling features that are already on",
    "translatedContent": "  - **「既に有効の場合は無効化しない」** - 既にオンの機能を再有効化せず接続リセットを防止"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "OhTBKdx9JUtfRDmBoIwdkU3OLKZKjdeCAeveqdEtDKc=",
    "originContent": "  - **\"Only if not manually set\"** - Respect manually enabled protection modes on unlock",
    "translatedContent": "  - **「手動設定の場合は無効化しない」** - ロック解除時に手動で有効化された保護モードを尊重"
  },
